Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.15,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(76,374)}吸菸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(294,626)}奇怪的店
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,574)}賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可憐 好不容易有點小錢卻沒地方花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只剩女人了吧
