Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 這方面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桐山親
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.06,0:05:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 請去別的地方玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像會長說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在成年之前我幫你保管吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.86,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用的時候隨時跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香子怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像經常去你那裡 有沒有給你添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有說嗎 果然吶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經完全不知道她在想什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親 姐姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸田八段 桐山五段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉能讓我拍張照嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 我該說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是父親如果知道這件事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐會變成什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我就沒有能做的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的庭院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到東京都內還有這樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:49.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池塘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼他們一直錯過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也好父親也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都不想割捨對方的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,宗谷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂我說 宗合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是主角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底跑到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看都淋濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是在旁邊的話就帶他過來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走 你也過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就要開始了 主角怎麼能在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒吸了一囗氣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.32,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不到他的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到他身影的那個瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界變得悄無聲息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的樣子沒有變
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.66,0:08:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像時間都停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記憶中有人在竊竊私語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他消失的那一瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長空劃破 沉重的雨傾盆而下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和那樣的人對局嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1130,714)}銀之線
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(128,298)}水面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.57,0:08:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.04,0:08:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他進入會場後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寂靜無聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人群分成兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真對不起大家 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他剛剛在庭院裡吶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠閒地看鯉魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼呀這是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那快開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宗谷 上台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十五歲 還是國中生就成為職業棋士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十一歲 成為取得頭銜的最年輕棋士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:37.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次次的刷新將棋界的歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史上首次取得全部的七大頭銜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之後經過十幾年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還是繼續穩坐在王座之上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的身影未曾變過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不褪色 不埋沒 一塵不染
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.89,0:09:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用壓倒性的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.02,0:10:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜靜地安坐在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他被比作神明的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有人說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有惡魔的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定是那樣的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來 有請島田八段發言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.54,0:10:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天雖然是工作日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻有眾多棋友到場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿到挑戰者資格已經過了三週
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都非常匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.66,0:10:43.96,Top,,0,0,0,,前夜祭結束前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田先生說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩局吶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那怪物對決首先要贏得兩局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則的話無法到達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第六局的會館
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:10:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島田開八段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獅子王七局比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一局 一百一十四手 認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟爸爸說了什麼不該說的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在郵件裡寫的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.19,0:11:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼也沒有說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.11,0:11:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不只剪了我的信用卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還逼問了一大堆問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讓我怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說我什麼都沒說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.91,0:11:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 不都是姐姐你自作自受嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作自受？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:49.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你憑什麼居高臨下的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以為自己是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只會畏畏縮縮的煩惱著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下著有氣無力的將棋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這些沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小桃？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明里姐…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們慢慢談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵架了 零…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零會被欺負了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在看起來有點忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女 是魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 豆皮壽司我們還是自己吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零碰上了麻煩的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰啊 那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近的 很照顧我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次是這家人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一副可憐的樣子融入進去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要弄得一團糟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鑽入別人的家中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焦躁不安 內心忐忑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.44,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到臉色慘白的零
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那張未曾見過的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.46,0:13:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一次都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我們提過的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 吃掉這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和姐姐做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雞蛋和芝麻都放了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很甜 非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了就有精神了 你一定要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什麼 真讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不是好人 那個女的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 日向 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行哦 這樣生氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.88,0:14:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一直一言不發呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也有點這麼覺得 只有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一點哦 只有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.12,0:14:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(1150,708)}水面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:15:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H5C5C5C\3c&Hffffff\pos(214,300)}青色的夜空下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆皮太甜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是甜點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這塊還放了切碎的醃芥末
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每塊都不一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.58,0:15:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就根本停不下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃胖了怎麼辦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自跟過來又擅自開動還要抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二層都是蔬菜系？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筑前煮？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:38.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像老太婆一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表現得太明顯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.77,0:15:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我很持家吧」之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單身男士對這種類型的都很饑渴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有秋葵和青花菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煮過後加上麻油和鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,韓式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 再不回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親做了晚餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裙子好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一吃飽就覺得想睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零 借我一件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有運動衫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才被爸爸罵過吧 快回家吶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好煩 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚點打個電話過去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別打開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於放鬆下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 是誰吶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個國中生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是那個人妻吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:10.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人妻是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 難道是說明里姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.95,0:17:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫明里嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她抱著的孩子是妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.46,0:17:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那三人是姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順便說一下 明里姐的年齡應該跟姐姐你差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那究竟是哪個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國中生還是那個大媽…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了…怎麼就扯上這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪個都不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你剛才說了…大媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…難道是那個幼稚園的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這變態
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:52.47,Top,,0,0,0,,你倒是快點回家啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了 我在零這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的在零這裡的話就沒意見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也已經沒電車了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.46,0:18:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 為什麼就不相信自己女兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經搞不懂香子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.01,0:18:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們真合得來呢 父親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 你之後有什麼打算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸很擔心你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸總是搞不清狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼「既然人家那麼照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把男朋友帶回來見個面」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我足足大了二十歲 有家室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更別說還是爸爸的師弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能帶回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會選擇那傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還想問呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小不點 竟然說我是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果真的是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會像現在這樣丟臉又辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 零 我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.79,0:19:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一整晚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手機微弱的光線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.43,0:19:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一次次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,微微映照出她的輪廓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是靜靜看著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個房間被染成了青藍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.53,0:20:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二人在深深的水下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一味下沉般的午夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說了聲「再見」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回一句嗯 卻又吞了回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天 我懷著破碎的心離開了那個家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.27,0:20:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,依舊如此 亳無改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無力改變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法成為姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒變成陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 你跑過來的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 當值日生花了點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值日生…好久沒聽過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個詞真讓人懷念吶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 你真的還是個學生吶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始二海堂等你都等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.31,0:21:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你來了 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我贏了哦 最後一局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來 我下季就跟你一樣是C1了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外態度也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人煩躁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼哼 重田選手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留級確定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還真是心跳加速呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我差點以為你就要跟我同一個級別了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思 你在哪裡看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是哪個將棋界的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這季我可是遊刃有餘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有壞消息就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這季也確定A級留任成功
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.77,0:21:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢 該說命懸一線呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.82,0:22:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是千鈞一髮程度的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:03.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鈞一髮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.53,0:22:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話從師兄口裡說出來就更沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 恭喜你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.87,0:22:10.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.66,0:22:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個都捂著眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.63,0:22:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於追上你了 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很期待跟你直接對決呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.59,0:22:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 對手喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.97,0:22:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說這話時的二海堂 神情太過耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.98,0:22:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我微閉雙目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼前又浮現出今早河邊的一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:15.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}川沿いを走る電車の音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}うつむいて咲く向日葵の色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}夕焼けがしましまのボーダーになる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}『ありがとう』って君がいうたんび
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}泣きそうな気持ちになるのはなんでだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}子供みたいにさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:41.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}涙なら冷蔵庫に置いてきたはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:44.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}勝ってうれしいはないちもんめ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.35,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}あの娘が欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:49.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}さよならバイスタンダー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}僕らは歩いて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.43,0:00:55.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}この道行きの最後が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:59.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}天国かそこらじゃあないとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:04.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}ただの君と笑って立っていたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}誇らしさとか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.86,0:01:07.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}願いとか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.32,0:01:11.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}希望とかもっとずっと持ち合わせとくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.76,0:01:17.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}こわくて　こわくて　こわくて　沈みそうでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:23.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}守るよ　守るよ　ぼくの全てを捧げ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:26.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}目の前の君に誓うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.27,0:00:15.19,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}沿著河邊開過的電車的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}俯下頭綻放的向日葵的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:22.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}晚霞化為一條條的紋樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:26.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}你每次說謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:30.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}為什麼都會感覺想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}像個孩子似的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:41.67,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}淚水應該已經留在冰箱裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:44.34,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}贏了好開心 笑容如花綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}想要獻給那個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:49.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}再見了旁觀者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:52.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}我們要前行
